<normalised orig="summe" auto="true">sum</normalised> is this therefore, To <normalised orig="conuert" auto="true">convert</normalised> any<lb/>
<normalised orig="poore" auto="true">poor</normalised> <normalised orig="soule" auto="true">soul</normalised> <normalised orig="vnto" auto="true">unto</normalised> God, or to make a<lb/>
