First, saith the Preacher, <quote type="biblical" ana="Eccl 9.11">The race is<lb/>
not to the swift.</quote> Asahel was as swift of foot as a roebuck, yet Abner met with<lb/>
him, smote him <normalised orig="vnder" auto="true">under</normalised> the <normalised orig="fift" auto="true">fifth</normalised> rib, &amp; slew<lb/>
